<h3 align=center>Quick Play Tab</h3>
<p>The Quick Play tab allows you to start playing a game as quickly as possible via Sierra Online.
Simply select your skill level (<i>novice</i> is the default), and click the <i>Play Now</i> button.
Any available games will be searched, and you will be joined to an appropriate game (if one exists).</p>

<p>If no appropriate game exists, a dialog will be displayed asking if you wish to host a game.  Click
<i>Ok</i> to host or <i>Cancel</i> to abort.  If an appropriate game is found, you will join and be
taken to the <a href="GameTab.html">Game</a> tab to begin the game.</p>

<p><b>Note: you must be connected to Internet in order to play games via Sierra Online.</b></p>

